2. About Us Page
Our Y-leaf Journey represents — from farm to your taste.
Zerothi was born from its origin in Nimar, Madhya Pradesh. It was a simple idea to bring
the real taste of Nimar to modern homes. We focus on purity, process, and consistency.
Coming from Nimar, where food is still rooted in tradition. We saw an opportunity to bring
that same real taste to a wider market.
Include :
