● BRAND JOURNEY - Zerothi is more than a food brand — it is a
representation of Nimar taste, its farmers, its women-led craftsmanship,
and a commitment to delivering real products made with honesty, tradition,
and purpose.
● VISION - Zerothi was founded with a vision to bring the taste of the Nimar
region to modern consumers while creating meaningful impact for local
communities connected to its roots.
● MISSION - Nimad is known for its rich agricultural heritage, hardworking
farmers, and traditional food culture. From banana farming to dairy-based
products, the region carries a unique identity that is rarely represented in
its purest form in the market. Zerothi was created to bridge that gap — by
delivering authentic, unadulterated products that truly represent the soil,
people, and traditions of Nimad.
